{"id":99,"count":4,"description":"Beautiful Kerala \u2013 Known as \u201cGod\u2019s Own Country\u201d, Kerala is a destination that blends lush greenery, tranquil backwaters, golden beaches, and misty hill stations into one unforgettable experience. From cruising on a traditional houseboat through the serene backwaters of Alleppey, to exploring the spice-scented plantations of Thekkady, and relaxing on the pristine beaches of Kovalam, Kerala offers something for every traveler. The rolling hills of Munnar with their endless tea gardens, the vibrant culture of Kochi with its historic charm, and the wildlife encounters in Periyar create a perfect balance of nature, culture, and adventure. With Ayurveda wellness retreats, colorful festivals, and warm hospitality, Kerala is a place where beauty, tradition, and serenity meet\u2014making it one of the most enchanting destinations in India.","link":"https:\/\/realtrips.thefuturecity.in\/destinations\/beautiful-kerala\/","name":"BEAUTIFUL KERALA","slug":"beautiful-kerala","taxonomy":"destination","parent":0,"meta":[],"thumbnail":{"width":900,"height":596,"file":"2025\/09\/Beautiful-kerala.png","filesize":1086893,"sizes":{"medium":{"file":"Beautiful-kerala-300x199.png","width":300,"height":199,"filesize":95841,"mime_type":"image\/png","source_url":"https:\/\/realtrips.thefuturecity.in\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/09\/Beautiful-kerala-300x199.png"},"thumbnail":{"file":"Beautiful-kerala-150x150.png","width":150,"height":150,"filesize":18757,"mime_type":"image\/png","source_url":"https:\/\/realtrips.thefuturecity.in\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/09\/Beautiful-kerala-150x150.png"},"medium_large":{"file":"Beautiful-kerala-768x509.png","width":768,"height":509,"filesize":497262,"mime_type":"image\/png","source_url":"https:\/\/realtrips.thefuturecity.in\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/09\/Beautiful-kerala-768x509.png"},"trip-thumb-size":{"file":"Beautiful-kerala-374x226.png","width":374,"height":226,"filesize":132214,"mime_type":"image\/p